    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The simple log processor passes all log records in a batch of 1 to the configured <ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1logs_1_1LogRecordExporter" kindref="compound">LogRecordExporter</ref>.</para>
<para>All calls to the configured <ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1logs_1_1LogRecordExporter" kindref="compound">LogRecordExporter</ref> are synchronized using a spin-lock on an atomic_flag. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
